comment:
* Base class for implementing a callback for the result of {@link
     * PrintDocumentAdapter#onWrite(PageRange[], ParcelFileDescriptor, CancellationSignal,
     * WriteResultCallback)}.

methods.name: public void onWriteFinished(PageRange[] pages)
methods.comment:
* Notifies that all the data was written. * * @param pages The pages that were written. Cannot be null * or empty.
* Returning {@link PageRange#ALL_PAGES} indicates that all pages that were * requested as the {@code pages} parameter in {@link #onWrite} were written.

methods.name: public void onWriteFailed(CharSequence error)
methods.comment: * Notifies that an error occurred while writing the data. * * @param error The localized error message. * shown to the user. May be null if error is unknown.

methods.name: public void onWriteCancelled()
methods.comment: * Notifies that write was cancelled as a result of a cancellation request.
